OL,3,CBank worker jailed after stealing over
OL,4,C#100,000
OL,6,FA bank worker from Flint has been
OL,7,Ffound guilty of stealing more than
OL,8,F#100,000 from her employer.
OL,10,FLesley Smith, a customer consultant
OL,11,Ffor Lloyds Banking Group, defrauded
OL,12,Fthe company out of the money by
OL,13,Fsending it to her own accounts.
OL,15,FSmith's offending began when she
OL,16,Ftransferred #200 into her own NatWest
OL,17,FBank account then larger amounts.
