OL,6,FThe court heard the payments included
OL,7,Feleven sums totalling #11,289.59 and
OL,8,F65 sums totalling #82,783 into her
OL,9,Faccounts.
OL,11,FBut NatWest "raised concerns" with
OL,12,FLloyds about the "exceptionally high"
OL,13,Fpayments given that her salary was
OL,14,Fonly #1,500 a month, said Prosecutor
OL,15,FJoseph Lees.
OL,17,FThe 44-year-old, gave some money to
OL,18,Fcharity and has repaid about #80,000,
OL,19,FMold Crown Court heard.
