OL,6,FNigel Horne, a senior investigator for
OL,7,FLloyds Banking Group, found the total
OL,8,Floss to Lloyds was #108,956,87.
OL,10,FMr Lees said the impact of Smith's
OL,11,Fcrimes led to greater scrutiny on her
OL,12,Fformer colleagues, worsening morale
OL,13,Fand slower efficiency in the bank.
OL,15,FSmith has now forfeited her pension -
OL,16,Fworth #86,180.74 - towards recouping
OL,17,Fthe losses.
