OL,6,FShe has also paid #120 in March 2025
OL,7,Fbut said she didn't pay more because
OL,8,Fshe thought it would "confuse" the
OL,9,Fcase, the court heard. Therefore
OL,10,FLloyds Banking Group's net loss is
OL,11,F#22,666.13.
OL,13,FCharlotte Cooper, defending Smith,
OL,14,Fsaid, "She made an entirely selfish
OL,15,Fdecision the day she decided to begin
OL,16,Fthis deception and there will be an
OL,17,Fimpact for the rest of her life."
