OL,6,FSmith, who has children aged 19 and
OL,7,F16, has not told her family about her
OL,8,Fpotential imprisonment today. She
OL,9,Fadded, "It's a clear and obvious case
OL,10,Fof head in the sand because she might
OL,11,Fnot be going home."
OL,13,FThe judge, His Honour Simon Mills told
OL,14,FSmith she had been in a "high position
OL,15,Fof trust and responsibility". He said
OL,16,Fit could be argued the sums were
OL,17,Frelatively small, in the context of
OL,18,FLloyds' assets, but her crimes changed
OL,19,Fthe way it operates.
