OL,6,FHe noted some of the stolen money went
OL,7,Fto charity but overall he said: "I
OL,8,Fsimply cannot understand why you did
OL,9,Fthis."
OL,11,FHe said he has to send her to prison
OL,12,Fbecause the offences are so serious.
OL,13,FBut he also said he found it "truly
OL,14,Fstaggering" that her family has no
OL,15,Fidea about her position in court and
OL,16,Fthat "a barrister - that's a stranger
OL,17,F- is going to have to make a phone
OL,18,Fcall" (to them).
